## Usage Examples

When a user asks:

- “Build a chatbot that answers FAQs from our veterinary clinic website in Spanish”:
  - Create a RAG chain based on the site content.
  - Use a Spanish system prompt reflecting the safety guidelines above.
  - Add a small demo script and usage instructions.

- “Add appointment booking to our existing vet bot”:
  - Design an appointment tool with clear input/output schema.
  - Expose it to the agent with a descriptive name and when-to-use guidance.
  - Update the system prompt to describe the new tool.
  - Add a test showing the bot booking an appointment with clarifying questions.

- “Make the bot remember each pet within a session”:
  - Add conversation memory (buffer or summary).
  - Ensure the system prompt encourages the model to reuse known details.
  - Optionally, introduce entity memory if there are stable identifiers available.
